{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/removing-return-to-cart-text-from-the-checkout-page","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1059,"date":"2021-07-21T08:52:24","date_gmt":"2021-07-21T08:52:24","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1059"},"modified":"2021-07-21T08:52:55","modified_gmt":"2021-07-21T08:52:55","slug":"removing-return-to-cart-text-from-the-checkout-page","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/removing-return-to-cart-text-from-the-checkout-page/","title":{"rendered":"Removing &#8220;return to cart&#8221; text from the checkout page"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The &#8220;return to cart&#8221; link found by default in all Shopify checkout pages can end up being a double edged sword: while some merchants may find it maximizes their conversions, others may disagree and wish they could be removed altogether. Regardless of who&#8217;s right, the good news is: it&#8217;s totally possible to do so and you can freely A/B test what works the best for you. <br><br>In this tutorial I&#8217;ll show you how to quickly remove the &#8220;return to cart&#8221; text from your Shopify checkout page.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-locating-the-text-and-removing-it\">Locating the text and removing it</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From your Shopify admin, navigate to <strong>online store > themes > actions > edit languages.</strong><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1581\" height=\"505\" class=\"wp-image-1065\" style=\"width: 650px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/edit_languages.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/edit_languages.jpg 1581w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/edit_languages-850x272.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/edit_languages-1200x383.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/edit_languages-768x245.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/edit_languages-1536x491.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1581px) 100vw, 1581px\" /></li><li>In the search bar at the top, right next to the button <strong>filters</strong>, type in the following: <em>return to cart</em><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1882\" height=\"754\" class=\"wp-image-1067\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/return123.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/return123.jpg 1882w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/return123-850x341.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/return123-1200x481.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/return123-768x308.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/return123-1536x615.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1882px) 100vw, 1882px\" /><br><br>Wait for it to load until you can see the fields as the image above.</li><li>Now, type one single space in the fields of &#8220;Back to Cart&#8221; and &#8220;Return to cart button label. <br><br>Once you do, hit &#8220;Save&#8221;, at the top right. <br><br>It should look fully white, like this:<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1555\" height=\"793\" class=\"wp-image-1069\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/return-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/return-2.jpg 1555w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/return-2-850x433.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/return-2-1200x612.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/return-2-768x392.jpg 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/return-2-1536x783.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1555px) 100vw, 1555px\" /></li><li>That is it &#8211; now your checkout page should no longer not show up the &#8220;return to cart&#8221;.<br></li></ol>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Learn how to quickly get rid of the &#8220;return to cart&#8221; text that shows up on the checkout page.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1062,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[206],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/remove_return_to_cart-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/remove_return_to_cart-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/remove_return_to_cart-1200x675.png","post_count":null,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["all themes"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1059"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/users/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/comments?post=1059"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1059/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1073,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/posts/1059/revisions/1073"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media/1062"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/media?parent=1059"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/categories?post=1059"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://www.ezfy.club/json/wp/v2/tags?post=1059"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["330429198"]}